в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ merged_final/            # вң… Production-ready merged model
в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ config.json          # Qwen2ForCausalLM config
в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җв”Җ model.safetensors    # ~1.9 GB merged weights
