в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җ scripts/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ benchmark_agent.py       # вң… Benchmark suite вҖ” runs all 5 crisis scenarios
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ train_dpo_gpu.py         # GPU DPO training script (local)
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ colab_train_dpo.py       # Colab-compatible training variant
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ merge_and_push_hf.py     # Merge LoRA вҶ’ safetensors + HF Hub push
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ deploy_space.py          # Deploy Gradio app to HF Spaces
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ run_simulation.py        # Single-scenario simulation runner
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ collect_episodes.py      # Episode data collection for DPO pairs
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ generate_dpo_fast.py     # Fast synthetic DPO pair generation
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ convert_healthcare.py    # MedMCQA/MedQA вҶ’ DPO format converter
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ export_metrics.py        # Export benchmark metrics to CSV/JSON
в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җ spaces/
в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ app.py                   # вң… Gradio demo (deployed to HF Spaces)
в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җ triage/
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ __init__.py
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ agents/
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ base_agent.py        # BaseAgent, TriageMessage, tool dispatch
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ specialized.py       # вң… All 6 specialized agent implementations
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ __init__.py
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ environment/
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ hospital_env.py      # HospitalCrisisEnv (OpenEnv-compatible)
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ reward_model.py      # Composite reward: survival + ICU + violations
в”Ӯ   в”Ӯ   в””в”Җв”Җ __init__.py
в”Ӯ   в”ңв”Җв”Җ training/
